                            const val = Number(e.target.value); 
                            setData(prev => { 
                              const newCredits = [...(prev.initialSetup.credits || [])]; 
                              const idx = newCredits.findIndex(c => String(c.accountId) === String(retainedEarningsId)); 
                              if (idx >= 0) { 
                                newCredits[idx] = { ...newCredits[idx], amount: val }; 
                              } else { 
                                newCredits.push({ accountId: retainedEarningsId, amount: val }); 
                              } 
                              return { ...prev, initialSetup: { ...prev.initialSetup, credits: newCredits } }; 
                            }); 
                            setIsDirty(true); 
                          }} 
                        />
                      </div>
                      <div className="text-[9px] font-black text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest pt-1 border-t mb-1">기초 부채 내역</div>
                      ${(initialSetup.credits || []).filter(r => String(r.accountId) !== String(retainedEarningsId)).map((r, i) => {
                        const originalIndex = initialSetup.credits.findIndex(c => c === r);
                        return html`
                          <div key=${originalIndex} className="flex gap-2 items-center">
                            <button onClick=${() => setActivePicker({ type: 'setupCredits', index: originalIndex })} className="flex-1 p-2.5 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 text-[11px] font-bold border border-slate-100 text-left truncate">${r.accountId ? getAccountById(r.accountId).name : '부채 선택'}</button>
                            <input type="number" className="w-20 sm:w-28 p-2 rounded-lg bg-white text-right font-black border border-slate-200 text-red-500 text-xs outline-none" value=${r.amount || ''} onChange=${(e) => { const val = Number(e.target.value); setData(prev => { const n = [...prev.initialSetup.credits]; n[originalIndex] = { ...n[originalIndex], amount: val }; return { ...prev, initialSetup: { ...prev.initialSetup, credits: n } }; }); setIsDirty(true); }} />
                            <button onClick=${()=>{ setData(prev => { const n = [...prev.initialSetup.credits]; n.splice(originalIndex, 1); return { ...prev, initialSetup: { ...prev.initialSetup, credits: n } }; }); setIsDirty(true); }} className="text-slate-300 hover:text-red-500 p-1"><${TrashIcon}/></button>
                          </div>
                        `;
                      })}
                      <button onClick=${() => { setData(prev => ({ ...prev, initialSetup: { ...prev.initialSetup, credits: [...(prev.initialSetup.credits || []), { accountId: '', amount: 0 }] } })); setIsDirty(true); }} className="w-full p-2 mt-1 text-[10px] font-black text-red-400 border border-dashed border-red-100 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-50">+ 부채 추가</button>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            `}
            ${settingsTab === 'accounts' && html`
              <div className="space-y-10">
                <div className="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                  ${['assets', 'liabilities'].map(cat => html`
                    <div key=${cat} className="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-2xl border shadow-inner h-fit text-slate-800">
                      <div className="flex justify-between items-center mb-3 text-indigo-500 font-black text-[10px] uppercase"><span>${cat.toUpperCase()} Accounts</span><button onClick=${() => setAddingToCategory(cat)} className="p-1 hover:bg-indigo-100 rounded-full transition-colors"><i data-lucide="plus" className="w-4 h-4"></i></button></div>
                      <div className="space-y-1.5">
                        ${(accounts[cat] || []).filter(a => a.name !== '이익잉여금').map(a => html`
                          <div key=${a.id} className="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 bg-white rounded-xl border group shadow-sm transition-all hover:border-indigo-200 font-bold">
                            <input className="flex-1 bg-transparent border-none outline-none font-bold text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-800" value=${a.name} onChange=${(e) => handleUpdateAccountName(cat, a.id, e.target.value)} />
                            <button onClick=${() => handleDeleteAccount(cat, a.id)} className="sm:opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 text-red-400 p-1.5"><${TrashIcon}/></button>
                          </div>
                        `)}
                        ${addingToCategory === cat && html`
                          <div className="p-1"><input autoFocus className="w-full p-2 bg-white rounded-xl border border-indigo-200 text-xs font-bold text-indigo-600 outline-none" placeholder="항목 입력 후 Enter" onBlur=${(e) => handleAddAccount(cat, e.target.value)} onKeyDown=${(e)=>e.key==='Enter'&&e.target.blur()} /></div>
                        `}
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  `)}
                </div>
                <div className="space-y-6">
                  ${['revenue', 'expenses'].map(type => html`
                    <div key=${type} className="border-t pt-5">
                      <div className="flex justify-between items-center mb-4"><h5 className="font-black text-indigo-600 uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px]">${type.toUpperCase()} 분류 관리</h5><button onClick=${() => setAddingToCategory(type)} className="text-[10px] bg-indigo-600 text-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full font-black shadow-sm">+ 추가</button></div>
                      <div className="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 sm:gap-4">
                        ${['fixed', 'variable'].map(subtype => html`
                          <div key=${subtype} onDragOver=${handleDragOver} onDrop=${() => handleSubtypeDrop(subtype, type)} className="bg-white border-2 border-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-5 transition-all shadow-sm min-h-[120px]">
                            <div className="flex justify-between items-center mb-3 border-b border-slate-50 pb-1.5 text-slate-400 font-black"><span className="uppercase text-[9px] tracking-widest">${subtype === 'fixed' ? '고정 (Fixed)' : '변동 (Variable)'}</span><i data-lucide=${subtype === 'fixed' ? 'lock' : 'zap'} className="w-3 h-3"></i></div>
                            <div className="grid grid-cols-1 gap-1.5">
                              ${accounts[type].filter(a => (a.subtype || 'fixed') === subtype).map(acc => html`
                                <div key=${acc.id} draggable onDragStart=${() => handleAccountDragStart(acc.id)} className="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold flex items-center gap-3 group hover:bg-white hover:border-indigo-100 transition-all text-slate-700 w-full shadow-sm">
                                  <i data-lucide="grip-vertical" className="text-slate-200 shrink-0 hidden sm:block"></i>
                                  <input className="bg-transparent border-none outline-none flex-1 font-bold min-w-0" value=${acc.name} onChange=${(e) => handleUpdateAccountName(type, acc.id, e.target.value)} />
                                  <button onClick=${() => handleDeleteAccount(type, acc.id)} className="sm:opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 text-red-400 p-1"><i data-lucide="x" className="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i></button>
                                </div>
                              `)}
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        `)}
                      </div>
                      ${addingToCategory === type && html`<div className="mt-3 p-3 bg-indigo-50 rounded-2xl border border-indigo-100 text-center"><input autoFocus className="bg-transparent border-none outline-none font-black text-indigo-600 text-center text-xs w-full" placeholder="항목 입력 후 Enter..." onBlur=${(e) => handleAddAccount(type, e.target.value)} onKeyDown=${(e)=>e.key==='Enter'&&e.target.blur()} /></div>`}
                    </div>
                  `)}
                </div>
              </div>
            `}
            ${settingsTab === 'editTransactions' && html`
              <div className="space-y-4 pb-10">
                <div className="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 bg-white p-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 text-slate-800 font-bold overflow-x-auto">
                  <i data-lucide="search" className="text-slate-300 w-4 h-4 shrink-0"></i><input type="date" className="bg-transparent outline-none font-bold text-[11px] cursor-pointer" value=${editRange.start} onChange=${(e)=>setEditRange({...editRange, start: e.target.value})}/><span className="text-slate-300">~</span><input type="date" className="bg-transparent outline-none font-bold text-[11px] cursor-pointer" value=${editRange.end} onChange=${(e)=>setEditRange({...editRange, end: e.target.value})}/>
                </div>
                <div className="space-y-2">
                  ${transactions.filter(t => t.date >= editRange.start && t.date <= editRange.end).sort((a,b) => b.date.localeCompare(a.date)).map(t => html`
                    <div key=${t.id} onClick=${()=>{setEditingTransaction(t); setEntryRows({date:t.date, debits:t.debits, credits:t.credits, memo:t.memo}); setIsEntryModalOpen(true);}} className="p-3.5 bg-white border rounded-xl flex justify-between cursor-pointer hover:border-indigo-500 transition-all shadow-sm active:bg-indigo-50">
                      <div><p className="text-[9px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase">${t.date}</p><p className="font-bold text-xs text-slate-700 mt-0.5">${t.memo || '거래 내역'}</p></div>
                      <div className="text-right flex flex-col justify-center"><div className="font-mono font-black text-slate-700 text-xs sm:text-base">${(t.debits.reduce((s,d)=>s+d.amount, 0)).toLocaleString()}원</div></div>
                    </div>
                  `)}
                </div>
              </div>
            `}
            ${isDirty && html`
              <div className="mt-6 md:hidden">
                <${Button} variant="primary" onClick=${handleSyncSettings} className="w-full bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 animate-pulse">설정 변경사항 저장하기<//>
              </div>
            `}
          </div>
        </div>
      <//>

      <${Modal} isOpen=${isEntryModalOpen} onClose=${() => {setIsEntryModalOpen(false); setEditingTransaction(null);}} title=${editingTransaction?"전표 수정":"전표 입력"} maxWidth="max-w-6xl" zIndex="z-[120]">
        <div className="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 text-slate-800">
          <div className="w-full lg:w-48 shrink-0 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-2xl border h-fit shadow-inner">
            <label className="block text-[9px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2 text-center lg:text-left">전표 날짜</label>
            <input type="date" className="w-full p-2.5 rounded-xl border text-xs font-bold outline-none mb-3 shadow-sm bg-white text-slate-700" value=${entryRows.date} onChange=${(e) => setEntryRows({...entryRows, date: e.target.value})} />
            ${editingTransaction && html`<button onClick=${handleDeleteTransactionWrapper} className="w-full p-3 bg-red-50 text-red-500 rounded-xl font-bold text-[11px] hover:bg-red-500 hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="trash-2" className="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>삭제하기</button>`}
          </div>
          <div className="flex-1 space-y-4 pb-20 sm:pb-0">
            <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div className="bg-white rounded-2xl border shadow-sm flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
                <div className="bg-indigo-600 text-white p-2 font-black text-center text-[10px] uppercase">Debit (차변)</div>
                <div className="p-3 space-y-2 min-h-[120px] sm:min-h-[250px] flex-1">
                  ${entryRows.debits.map((r, i) => html`
                    <div key=${i} className="flex gap-1.5 items-center animate-in slide-in-from-left-2">
                      <button onClick=${() => setActivePicker({ type: 'debits', index: i })} className="flex-1 p-2.5 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 text-[11px] font-bold border border-slate-100 text-left truncate active:bg-indigo-50">${r.accountId ? getAccountById(r.accountId).name : '계정 선택'}</button>
                      <input type="number" className="w-20 sm:w-28 p-2 rounded-lg bg-white text-right font-black border border-slate-200 text-xs outline-none" placeholder="0" value=${r.amount || ''} onChange=${(e) => handleUpdateEntryRow('debits', i, 'amount', Number(e.target.value))} />
                      <button onClick=${()=>{const n=[...entryRows.debits]; if(n.length>1){n.splice(i,1); setEntryRows(prev => ({...prev, debits:n}));}}} className="text-slate-300 hover:text-red-500 p-1"><${TrashIcon}/></button>
                    </div>
                  `)}
                  <button onClick=${() => setEntryRows(prev => ({...prev, debits: [...prev.debits, {accountId:'', amount:0}]}))} className="w-full p-2 mt-1 text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 border border-dashed border-indigo-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-50">+ 행 추가</button>
                </div>
                <div className="bg-slate-50 p-2.5 flex justify-between items-center font-black border-t text-xs sm:text-base">
                  <span className="text-[9px] uppercase text-slate-400">Total Debit</span>
                  ${totalCreditSum > totalDebitSum && html`
                    <span className="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-red-500 font-black px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-red-50 border border-red-100 animate-pulse">
                      ${(totalCreditSum - totalDebitSum).toLocaleString()}원 부족
                    </span>
                  `}
                  <span className="font-mono text-indigo-600 font-black">${totalDebitSum.toLocaleString()}원</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div className="bg-white rounded-2xl border shadow-sm flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
                <div className="bg-red-500 text-white p-2 font-black text-center text-[10px] uppercase">Credit (대변)</div>
                <div className="p-3 space-y-2 min-h-[120px] sm:min-h-[250px] flex-1">
                  ${entryRows.credits.map((r, i) => html`
                    <div key=${i} className="flex gap-1.5 items-center animate-in slide-in-from-right-2">
                      <button onClick=${() => setActivePicker({ type: 'credits', index: i })} className="flex-1 p-2.5 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 text-[11px] font-bold border border-slate-100 text-left truncate active:bg-red-50">${r.accountId ? getAccountById(r.accountId).name : '계정 선택'}</button>
                      <input type="number" className="w-20 sm:w-28 p-2 rounded-lg bg-white text-right font-black border border-slate-200 text-xs outline-none" placeholder="0" value=${r.amount || ''} onChange=${(e) => handleUpdateEntryRow('credits', i, 'amount', Number(e.target.value))} />
                      <button onClick=${()=>{const n=[...entryRows.credits]; if(n.length>1){n.splice(i,1); setEntryRows(prev => ({...prev, credits:n}));}}} className="text-slate-300 hover:text-red-500 p-1"><${TrashIcon}/></button>
                    </div>
                  `)}
                  <button onClick=${() => setEntryRows(prev => ({...prev, credits: [...prev.credits, {accountId:'', amount:0}]}))} className="w-full p-2 mt-1 text-[10px] font-black text-red-500 border border-dashed border-red-200 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-50">+ 행 추가</button>
                </div>
                <div className="bg-slate-50 p-2.5 flex justify-between items-center font-black border-t text-xs sm:text-base">
                  <span className="text-[9px] uppercase text-slate-400">Total Credit</span>
                  ${totalDebitSum > totalCreditSum && html`
                    <span className="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-red-500 font-black px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-red-50 border border-red-100 animate-pulse">
                      ${(totalDebitSum - totalCreditSum).toLocaleString()}원 부족
                    </span>
                  `}
                  <span className="font-mono text-red-500 font-black">${totalCreditSum.toLocaleString()}원</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div className="bg-slate-50 p-3 sm:p-4 rounded-2xl border flex flex-col gap-3 shadow-inner">
              <input type="text" className="w-full bg-white p-2.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 outline-none font-bold placeholder:text-slate-300 text-slate-700 text-xs sm:text-base" placeholder="거래 메모를 입력하세요 (예: 식비 결제)" value=${entryRows.memo} onChange=${(e) => setEntryRows({...entryRows, memo: e.target.value})} />
              <div className="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
                <span className=${`px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase shadow-sm ${totalDebitSum === totalCreditSum && totalDebitSum > 0 ? 'bg-emerald-500 text-white' : 'bg-slate-200 text-slate-500'}`}>
                  ${totalDebitSum === totalCreditSum && totalDebitSum > 0 
                    ? '차대일치' 
                    : `불일치 (${Math.abs(totalDebitSum - totalCreditSum).toLocaleString()}원 부족)`}
                </span>
                <button onClick=${handleSaveEntry} disabled=${isSavingEntry || totalDebitSum !== totalCreditSum || totalDebitSum === 0} className="flex-1 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 disabled:bg-slate-300 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-black shadow-lg transition-all active:scale-95 text-xs sm:text-sm whitespace-nowrap">
                  ${isSavingEntry ? html`
                    <span className="flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                      <i data-lucide="loader-2" className="w-4 h-4 animate-spin"></i> 저장 중...
                    </span>
                  ` : "전표 저장하기"}
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <//>

      <${Modal} isOpen=${activePicker !== null} onClose=${() => setActivePicker(null)} title="계정과목 선택" maxWidth="max-w-4xl" zIndex="z-[150]">
        <${AccountGridPicker} accounts=${accounts} onPick=${handleAccountPick} />
      <//>
    </div>
  `;
};

const Root = () => html`
  <${ErrorBoundary}>
    <${App} />
  <//>
`;

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(html`<${Root} />`);
</script>
</body>
</html>
